(381, 1, '2012-06-10 17:55:48', '2012-06-10 21:55:48', 'ISE CULTURAL FOUNDATION is pleased to present "Art Student Exhibition in NY". This exhibition offers art students a place to exhibit their artwork in SOHO. We are exhibiting all submitted artworks by art students from all over the world. ISE Cultural Foundation will invite the celebrated art professionals as Jurors, who will be awarding selected works at the Award Ceremony/Closing Party after the exhibition. Also, the New York City Audience Award will be determined by the votes of the audience. No Selection. ISE Cultural Foundation exhibit all artworks received.\r\n\r\nFor detailed informations please get on line:\r\n<a href="http://iseny.org/usr_helio1/page_g_c_summer_student.php" target="_blank">http://iseny.org/usr_helio1/page_g_c_summer_student.php</a>', 'ISE Cultural Foundation will host "Art Student Exhibition in NY 2012"', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ise-cultural-foundation-will-host-art-student-exhibition-in-ny-2012', '', '', '2012-08-16 18:15:20', '2012-08-16 22:15:20', '', 0, 'http://tpecc-ny.org/?p=381', 0, 'post', '', 0),
