(496, 1, '2012-06-17 10:43:27', '2012-06-17 14:43:27', 'June 28, 29, 30, 2012 at 8:00pm\r\nJuly 1, 2012 at 3:00pm\r\nRuth Page Center for the Arts\r\n1016 North Dearborn Street, Chicago, IL 60610\r\nTel: 312.337.6543 Web: <a href="http://www.ruthpage.org/" target="_blank">www.ruthpage.org</a>\r\n\r\nThe whole June of 2012, WCdance and its energetic dancers are leaving Taiwan to Chicago, developing a new contemporary dance work with The Seldoms, a Chicago-based dance company, during their residency. To both WCdance and The Seldoms, there are some values and goals they share together: innovation; invested collaboration with artists of other disciplines; excellent technical dancing; and particular interest in the visual environment of the stage space. In this time, they will definitely create a new spectacle of dance on the stage. The Artistic Director of WCdance, WenChung Lin, will also teach master classes open to the Chicago dance community.', '《SMALL 》SERIES & HIS FRIENDS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e3%80%8asmall-%e3%80%8bseries-his-friends', '', '', '2012-08-17 10:45:23', '2012-08-17 14:45:23', '', 0, 'http://tpecc-ny.org/?p=496', 0, 'post', '', 0),
