(629, 1, '2005-03-17 17:35:38', '2005-03-17 21:35:38', 'Sunday, January 9, 2005 at 7:00 pm\r\nLila Acheson Wallance Auditorium at Japan Society\r\n333 East 47th Street, New York, NY 10017\r\nPhone: 212.832.1155\r\nwww.japansociety.org\r\n<strong>PERFORMING ARTS FROM TAIWAN 2005</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>The Legend Lin Dance Theater</strong>\r\nArtistic Director: Lee-Chen LIN\r\nInspired by traditional religious rituals and ceremonial rites celebrating the rhythms of nature and our place in it, Lee-Chen Lin''s artistry combines a lush visual aesthetics with a brilliantly original and exquisitely languid choreography that gives new meaning to the phrase "poetry in motion." Anthem to the fading Flowers pays tribute to the cycle of the year and the complementary principles of Yun and Yang, whose eternal struggle provides the driving force behind the changing of the seasons.', 'SHOWCASE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'showcase', '', '', '2012-08-17 17:41:43', '2012-08-17 21:41:43', '', 0, 'http://tpecc-ny.org/?p=629', 0, 'post', '', 0),
