(697, 1, '2006-04-17 22:27:46', '2006-04-18 02:27:46', 'July 14 - August 19, 9am - 11pm\r\n\r\nThe Taiwan Today Festival continues with Starry Sky, the largest kite exhibition ever presented in North America. Award- winning kite master and designer Buteo Huang has created a dazzling collection of hundreds of hand-made kites. Made from space-age materials, the collection features 307 kites.\r\n\r\nClick below for more information:\r\nIntroduction\r\nSchedule', 'STARRY SKY KITE EXHIBITION BY BUTEO HUANG', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'starry-sky-kite-exhibition-by-buteo-huang', '', '', '2012-08-17 22:30:37', '2012-08-18 02:30:37', '', 0, 'http://tpecc-ny.org/?p=697', 0, 'post', '', 0),
