(1321, 1, '2009-01-30 23:18:45', '2009-01-31 03:18:45', 'January 17 - 27, 2009\r\n\r\nThe Happy Puppetry Company and New Happy Puppetry Company are directed by Taiwan''s leading female puppeteer, Mrs. Ko Chiang, Szu-mei, with her son, Ko, Chia-Tsai, and grandson, Ko Shih-hung, serving as puppeteers. Since the Company''s establishment in 1967, it has traveled all over Taiwan putting on performances of traditional puppetry at temple fairs and in rural communities.\r\n\r\nClick below for more information:\r\nIntroduction\r\nSchedule', 'THE HAPPY PUPPETRY COMPANY FROM TAIWAN', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-happy-puppetry-company-from-taiwan-2', '', '', '2012-08-21 23:32:48', '2012-08-22 03:32:48', '', 0, 'http://tpecc-ny.org/?p=1321', 0, 'post', '', 0),
